subject: Cycling, Road
Cycling, Track
lead_paragraph: The Swiss rookie Stefan Küng rode to an impressive solo victory on the rain-soaked Tour of Romandie’s 105.5-mile fourth stage from La Neuveville to Fribourg in Switzerland.
